<script>
  if (document.querySelector('.oc-container'))
  {
    window._oc = window._oc || {};
    window._oc.account = "{{OMQ Account}}";
    window._oc.apikey = "{{OMQ Help Api Key}}";
    window._oc.language = "{{OMQ Language}}";
    window._oc.maxQuestions = 5;
    window._oc.inputAttr = {
        placeholder: '{{QMQ Help Input Placeholder}}'
    };
    (function () {
        var oc = document.createElement('script');
        oc.type = 'text/javascript';
        oc.async = true;
        oc.src = "https://assets.omq.de/os/os.min.js";
        var s = document.getElementsByTagName('script')[0];
        s.parentNode.insertBefore(oc, s);
    })();
  }
</script>

<script>
  if (document.querySelector('.os-container')) {
    window._os = window._os || {};
    window._os.account = "{{OMQ Account}}";
    window._os.apikey = "{{OMQ Contact Api Key}}";
    window._os.language = "{{OMQ Language}}";

    (function () {
        var os = document.createElement("script");
        os.type = "text/javascript";
        os.async = true;
        os.src = "https://{{OMQ Account}}.omq.de/os/os.min.js";
        var s = document.getElementsByTagName("script")[0];
        s.parentNode.insertBefore(os, s);
    })();
  }
</script>
